    "body" : "<p>No, using 1.8 features in your source code requires you to target a 1.8 VM. I just tried the new Java 8 release and tried compiling with <code>-target 1.7 -source 1.8</code>, and the compiler refuses:</p>\n\n<pre><code>$ javac Test -source 1.8 -target 1.7\njavac: source release 1.8 requires target release 1.8\n</code></pre>\n"
